{"tid":1763741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中大民調】主要訴求全線下滑ㅤ矛頭仍然指向政府","createTime":"2019-11-30T14:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T10:50:06.000Z","uid":201801,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad49be61e8f81ea5d0975c2dc27bed339689b3a","tid":1763741,"uid":201801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"調查橫跨區選進行（21-26/11），<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會、重組警隊、林鄭下台等訴求各下跌4-5%。<br />\n八成受訪者認同要再搞對話平台。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91%E1%85%A0%E7%9F%9B%E9%A0%AD%E4%BB%8D%E7%84%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%90%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C/?fbclid=IwAR1SiW1qTTcemNXmL7vfjXiJSH0gS0tUwjF_GPbQaIIILGvSzT0O4uQgVL0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B7%259A%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%25BB%2591%25E1%2585%25A0%25E7%259F%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%2584%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1SiW1qTTcemNXmL7vfjXiJSH0gS0tUwjF_GPbQaIIILGvSzT0O4uQgVL0&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=fc5543fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B7%259A%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%25BB%2591%25E1%2585%25A0%25E7%259F%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%2584%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1SiW1qTTcemNXmL7vfjXiJSH0gS0tUwjF_GPbQaIIILGvSzT0O4uQgVL0&h=e33d2778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91%E1%85%A0%E7%9F%9B%E9%A0%AD%E4%BB%8D%E7%84%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%90%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C/?fbclid=IwAR1SiW1qTTcemNXmL7vfjXiJSH0gS0tUwjF_GPbQaIIILGvSzT0O4uQgVL0</a><br />\n