:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"區選後技術性反彈<br />\n不過都要注意"},{"pid":"49fad9ffa2b189453767ad4b3aebfd0ad4ec37ef","tid":1763741,"uid":34863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔搞返啲野, 真係有堆on9覺得區選贏咗就叫平息"},{"pid":"7d18873674e95cd97cf2259aaa34b93361421c8d","tid":1763741,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府爭住開紅隧, 回復黨鐵, 務求令社會回復平願等大家自動散水<br />\n話左唔可以休息架喇</span>"},{"pid":"91f34cc9a321e9f73a0673e6b06c85a46f6800e0","tid":1763741,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"其實一路話訴求支持比例下滑, 一路睇返移民比例上升緊<br />\n即係有一班典型港豬心態係, 咩抗爭手街我唔理喇我都移民嚕"},{"pid":"1518bb4170e87212f24fa4597c9be7a2d43ac277","tid":1763741,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T00:17:55.000Z","msg":"大家睇清楚#1的時間點。係比較緊10月同11月呀! 中間民意下跌少少, 估計係因為黎明行動呀!<br />\n<br />\n而民意下跌少少之影響已經在區議會選舉反映出來。<br />\n<br />\n呢d已經被市場消化之舊資訊,仲去反芻？立場記者下次唔好俾人利用啦！！！！"},{"pid":"3d5060eb5a2245bb5fad8dc3a26696ee885952fd","tid":1763741,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"法定獨立調查的支持度仍然極高，達 84%，但比一個月前的 88% 已有所下跌。重組警隊方面，支持比例由 69% 跌到 64%，同時反對比例有大幅增長。至於林鄭下台，則由 73% 跌到 69%，跌幅和前面兩條差不多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_mfzqO_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_mfzqO_1200x0.png&h=9a08fb24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 和首十條問題一樣，這次的回應也顯示了親政府陣營有鞏固，多項數據都向政府方向移動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1232/1*xAGdM_NOtTaJKIp_3RiTGg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1232%2F1%2AxAGdM_NOtTaJKIp_3RiTGg.png&h=693e7a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 不過總的來說，市民對政府仍然極度不滿，也普遍認為政府要為抗爭帶來的後果負責。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1232/1*I18xyfOpGUMdK_sxu_Rt5Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1232%2F1%2AI18xyfOpGUMdK_sxu_Rt5Q.png&h=2eaf6c42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 經過多個月的抗爭，市民漸漸認為抗爭不會因為打壓而減退，開始預期政府會讓步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1232/1*boM4HcoOFX1HxB7kuvNjzA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1232%2F1%2AboM4HcoOFX1HxB7kuvNjzA.png&h=695b1f36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次調查於 11 月 21 日至 26 日進行，剛好跨過了區議會選舉。"}]}